00%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235971568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Athens-based%20boutique%20film%20outfit%20Heretic%20has%20two%20titles%20in%20the%20Cannes%20ACID%20(Association%20for%20the%20International%20Distribution%20of%20Independent%20Cinemas)%20sidebar.%20Heretic%E2%80%99s%20own%20Greek%20production%2C%20co-produced%20with%20North%20Macedonia%E2%80%99s%20List%20Production%2C%20%E2%80%9CKyuka%20Before%20Summer%E2%80%99s%20End%2C%E2%80%9D%20by%20debut%20director%20Kostas%20Charamountanis%2C%20is%20the%20opening%20film%20of%20the%20ACID%20program.%20The%20film%20follows%20a%20family%20of%20three%2C%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fheretic-cannes-acid-2024-1235971568%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fheretic-cannes-acid-2024-1235971568%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fheretic-cannes-acid-2024-1235971568%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Are%20Not%20So%20Innocent...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Ramdev%20In%20Patanjali%20Ads%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20and%20his%20aide%20Balkrishna%20are%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20as%20it%20hears%20the%20contempt%20case%20against%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20misleading%20ads%20and%20Covid%20cure%20claims.%20The%20court%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Patanjali%20founders%20during%20the%20previous%20hearing%20last%20week.%20It%20had%20also%20pulled%20up%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20for%20not%20acting%20against%20the%20Haridwar-based%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20called%20the%20Patanjali%20founders%20forward%20and%20told%20them%20they%20have%20made%20significant%20contribution%20to%20yoga.%20%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20what%20you%20have%20done%20for%20yoga%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%20The%20two%20have%20said%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20offer%20a%20public%20apology.%C2%A0Ramdev%20said%20it%20was%20never%20his%20intention%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20pointed%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Battitude%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20shot%20down%20other%20systems%20of%20medicine%20to%20stress%20the%20benefits%20of%20Ayurveda.%C2%A0Justice%20Amanullah%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Blaw%20is%20the%20same%20for%20everybody%26quot%3B.%20Ramdev%20replied%20that%20he%20would%20be%20careful%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20will%20consider%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20light%20of%20all%20the%20earlier%20developments.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20decided%20whether%20to%20forgive%20you%20or%20not.%20You%20have%20violated%20(directives)%20thrice.%20The%20earlier%20orders%20are%20under%20our%20consideration.%20You%20are%20not%20so%20innocent%20that%20you%20did%20not%20know%20what's%20happening%20in%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20next%20hearing%20will%20be%20held%20on%20April%2023.%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20court%20again%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20demonstrate%20their%20intent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20outside%20the%20court%2C%20Ramdev%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20what%20I%20had%20to.%20I%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20earlier%20rejected%20two%20sets%20of%20apologies%20by%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20letters%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20media%20first.%20%26quot%3BTill%20the%20matter%20hit%20the%20court%2C%20the%20contemnors%20did%20not%20find%20it%20fit%20to%20send%20us%20the%20affidavits.%20They%20believe%20in%20publicity%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20A%20Amanullah%2C%20also%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20asked%20if%20the%20apology%20is%20%26quot%3Beven%20heartfelt%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTendering%20apology%20is%20not%20enough.%20You%20should%20suffer%20the%20consequences%20for%20violating%20the%20court's%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20Covid%20years%2C%20when%20Patanjali%20launched%20a%20drug%2C%20Coronil%2C%20in%202021%20and%20Ramdev%20described%20it%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20evidence-based%20medicine%20for%20COVID-19%26quot%3B.%20The%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20spoke%20out%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20lie%26quot%3B%20that%20Coronil%20had%20WHO%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20a%20video%20of%20Ramdev%2C%20in%20which%20he%20was%20heard%20saying%20that%20allopathy%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstupid%20and%20bankrupt%20science%26quot%3B%2C%20went%20viral.%20He%20said%20no%20modern%20medicine%20was%20curing%20Covid.%20The%20IMA%20sent%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20Ramdev%20and%20sought%20an%20apology%20and%20withdrawal%20of%20statements.%20Patanjali%20Yogpeeth%20responded%20that%20Ramdev%20was%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20forwarded%20WhatsApp%20message%20and%20has%20no%20ill-will%20against%20modern%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20IMA%20moved%20a%20petition%20against%20Patanjali%20after%20it%20published%20an%20advertisement%20in%20newspapers%20titled%20'Misconceptions%20Spread%20By%20Allopathy%3A%20Save%20Yourself%20And%20The%20Country%20From%20The%20Misconceptions%20Spread%20By%20Pharma%20And%20Medical%20Industry'.%20The%20ad%20claimed%20that%20Patanjali%20drugs%20had%20cured%20people%20of%20diabetes%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20thyroid%2C%20liver%20cirrhosis%2C%20arthritis%20and%20asthma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%2C%20systematic%2C%20and%20unabated%20spread%20of%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20comes%20alongside%20Patanjali's%20efforts%20to%20make%20false%20claims%20about%20curing%20certain%20diseases%20through%20use%20of%20Patanjali%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2021%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20warned%20Patanjali%20against%20claims%20that%20its%20products%20can%20completely%20cure%20ailments%20such%20as%20diabetes%20and%20high%20blood%20pressure%20and%20threatened%20to%20slap%20heavy%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatanjali's%20counsel%2C%20court%20documents%20say%2C%20then%20assured%20that%20%26quot%3Bhenceforth%2C%20there%20shall%20not%20be%20any%20violation%20of%20any%20of%20the%20laws%2C%20especially%20relating%20to%20advertisement%20and%20branding%20of%20products%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2015%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20received%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-balkrishna-ramdev-from-covid-cure-claim-to-an-anonymous-letter-how-patanjali-case-unfolded-5417538%5C%22%3Eanonymous%20letter%20%3C%2Fa%3Eaddressed%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20with%20copies%20marked%20to%20Justice%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20Amanullah.%20The%20letter%20mentioned%20misleading%20advertisements%20Patanjali%20continued%20to%20put%20out.%20IMA's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20PS%20Patwalia%2C%20also%20showed%20the%20court%20newspaper%20advertisements%20after%20the%20November%2021%2C%202023%20warning%20and%20transcript%20of%20a%20press%20conference%20by%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20right%20after%20the%20court's%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sought%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20company%20on%20why%20contempt%20proceedings%20should%20not%20be%20initiated.%20In%20strong%20remarks%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcountry%20is%20being%20taken%20for%20a%20ride%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Bsitting%20with%20its%20eyes%20shut%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2019%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told%20that%20Patanjali%20had%20not%20filed%20the%20reply%20to%20the%20contempt%20notice.%20It%20then%20asked%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20to%20appear%20in%20person.%20The%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20in%20its%20April%202%20hearing%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20defiance%26quot%3B%20over%20not%20filing%20proper%20affidavits%20over%20the%20misleading%20advertisements.%20The%20court%20told%20them%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bready%20for%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20apology%20is%20not%20persuading%20this%20court.%20It%20is%20more%20of%20a%20lip%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20rejecting%20their%20apology%2C%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20file%20affidavits%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20set%20of%20apologies%20was%20rejected%20on%20April%2010%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20the%20court%20noted%20that%20they%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20media%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713251880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5v2rp03o_ramdev-ani-_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-patanjali-their-apologies-rejected-ramdev-and-aides-big-supreme-court-date-today-5452102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20and%20his%20aide%20Balkrishna%20are%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20as%20it%20hears%20the%20contempt%20case%20against%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20misleading%20ads%20and%20Covid%20cure%20claims%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-patanjali-their-apologies-rejected-ramdev-and-aides-big-supreme-court-date-today-5452102%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-pa