ai%20with%20a%20sturdy%2070-run%20stand%20in%20seven%20overs%20with%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20who%20raced%20to%2023%20off%2015%20balls%20(3x4s%2C%201x6s).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20MI%20on%20charge%2C%20pacer%20Pathirana%20produced%20a%20two-wicket%20over%20after%20the%20powerplay%20accounting%20for%20Kishan%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20(0)%2C%20getting%20him%20caught%20at%20third%20man%20with%20Mustafizur%20Rahman%20producing%20a%20juggling%20act%20at%20the%20ropes%20to%20complete%20the%20catch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETilak%20Varma%20aided%20Rohit%20with%20a%2020-ball%2031%20laced%20with%20five%20fours%2C%20adding%2060%20off%2038%20balls%20for%20the%20third%20wicket%2C%20but%20Pathirana's%20return%20broke%20their%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Mumbai%20duo%20of%20Shardul%20Thakur%20and%20Tushar%20Deshpande%20tilted%20the%20game%20in%20favour%20of%20CSK%2C%20producing%20two%20tight%20overs%20which%20broke%20the%20back%20of%20MI's%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20fell%20for%20just%20two%20but%20consumed%20six%20balls%20and%20Tim%20David%20hammered%20a%20couple%20of%20sixes%20but%20failed%20to%20capitalise.%20Amid%20all%20this%2C%20Rohit%20remained%20stuck%20at%20the%20other%20end%20watching%20the%20game%20slip%20away%20despite%20his%20best%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier.%20Dhoni's%20ballistic%2020%20garnished%20forceful%20fifties%20by%20Shivam%20Dube%20and%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20as%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20powered%20to%20a%20strong%20206%20for%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDube%20(66%20not%20out%2C%2010x4%2C%202x6)%20and%20Gaikwad%20(69)%2C%20who%20milked%2090%20runs%20off%20a%20mere%2045%20balls%20for%20the%20third%20wicket%2C%20gave%20Chennai%20innings%20steam%20in%20the%20initial%20and%20middle%20passages%20of%20the%20play%20before%20Dhoni%20mesmerized%20a%20packed%20Wankhede%20with%20vintage%20shot-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20CSK%20skipper%20hammered%20three%20consecutive%20sixes%20off%20MI%20skipper%20Pandya%20(2%2F43)%20to%20help%20his%20side%20collect%2026%20runs%20off%20the%20final%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni's%20stunning%20knock%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20the%20balls%20sailing%20over%20long-off%2C%20wide%20long-on%20and%20deep%20square%20leg%20%E2%80%93%20also%20pushed%20Chennai%20past%20the%20200-run%20mark%2C%20which%20did%20appear%20tough%20until%20that%20final%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20he%20could%20not%20push%20beyond%2069%2C%20which%20came%20off%2040%20balls%20with%20five%20sixes%20and%20as%20many%20boundaries%2C%20Gaikwad%20appeared%20in%20prime%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSK%20skipper%20hit%20through%20the%20line%20effortlessly%20to%20clear%20ropes%20and%20when%20the%20MI%20bowlers%20challenged%20him%20by%20angling%20their%20deliveries%20into%20his%20body%2C%20Gaikwad%20improvised%20to%20find%20his%20runs%20without%20taking%20any%20unwanted%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713250320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2eq2bt7g_ms-dhoni-and-rohit-sharma_625x300_15_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fms-dhonis-gesture-for-heartbroken-rohit-sharma-is-another-sixer-on-internet-5442383%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20looked%20to%20lift%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20morale%20after%20the%20latter's%20ton%20went%20in%20vain%20during%20the%20MI%20vs%20CSK%20match%20in%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRight%20To%20Sleep%20Is%20Basic%20Requirement%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20On%20Questioning%20Post%20Midnight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20to%20sleep%20is%20a%20basic%20human%20requirement%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20violated%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20said%20on%20Monday%20deprecating%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20questioning%20a%20senior%20citizen%20throughout%20the%20night%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Revati%20Mohite-Dere%20and%20Manjusha%20Deshpande%20said%20statements%20must%20be%20recorded%20during%20earthly%20hours%20and%20not%20at%20night%20when%20a%20person's%20cognitive%20skills%20may%20be%20impaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20gave%20the%20order%20in%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%2064-year-old%20Ram%20Issrani%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20probe%20agency%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20arrested%20Issrani%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20plea%2C%20Issrani%20claimed%20that%20his%20arrest%20was%20illegal%20and%20unwarranted%20as%20he%20had%20been%20cooperating%20with%20the%20probe%20and%20had%20appeared%20before%20the%20agency%20whenever%20he%20was%20issued%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%207%2C%202023%2C%20Issrani%20appeared%20before%20the%20agency%20as%20per%20the%20summons%20issued%2C%20and%20he%20was%20questioned%20throughout%20the%20night%20and%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20plea%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20but%20said%20it%20disapproved%20of%20the%20practice%20of%20questioning%20the%20petitioner%20through%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency's%20counsel%2C%20Hiten%20Venegaonkar%2C%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20Issrani%20had%20consented%20to%20his%20statement%20being%20recorded%20through%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20plea%2C%20Issrani%20was%20questioned%20till%203%20am%20by%20ED%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoluntary%20or%20otherwise%2C%20we%20deprecate%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20petitioner's%20statement%20was%20recorded%20so%20late%20in%20the%20night%2C%20which%20went%20on%20post%20midnight%20till%203.30%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'right%20to%20sleep'%20%2F%20'right%20to%20blink'%20is%20a%20basic%20human%20requirement%2C%20inasmuch%20as%2C%20non-providing%20of%20the%20same%2C%20violates%20a%20person's%20human%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELack%20of%20sleep%20affects%20a%20person's%20health%20and%20may%20impair%20his%20mental%20faculties%2C%20cognitive%20skills%20and%20so%20on%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20said%20person%2C%20so%20summoned%2C%20cannot%20be%20deprived%20of%20his%20basic%20human%20right%20i.e.%20right%20to%20sleep%2C%20by%20the%20agency%2C%20beyond%20a%20reasonable%20time.%20Statements%20must%20necessarily%20be%20recorded%20during%20earthly%20hours%20and%20not%20in%20the%20night%20when%20the%20person's%20cognitive%20skills%20may%20be%20impaired%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20when%20a%20person%20is%20summoned%20for%20questioning%2C%20the%20investigating%20agency%20was%20yet%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Breason%20to%20believe%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20said%20person%20is%20guilty%20of%20an%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20petitioner%20had%20appeared%20before%20the%20agency%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20could%20have%20been%20summoned%20on%20some%20other%20day%20or%20even%20the%20next%20day%20instead%20of%20keeping%20him%20waiting%20after%20midnight%2C%20despite%20his%20alleged%20consent%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsent%20is%20immaterial.%20Recording%20of%20statement%2C%20at%20unearthly%20hours%2C%20definitely%20results%20in%20the%20deprivation%20of%20a%20person's%20sleep%2C%20a%20basic%20human%20right%20of%20an%20individual.%20We%20disapprove%20of%20this%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20deems%20it%20appropriate%20to%20direct%20the%20ED%20to%20issue%20a%20circular%2Fdirections%20about%20the%20timings%20to%20record%20statements%20when%20summons%20are%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20compliance%20on%20September%209.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713250260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F85mh9qus_bombay-high-court-website-photo_625x300_20_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-post-midnight-questioning-by-central-agency-bombay-high-courts-violation-of-rights-reminder-5448540%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20right%20to%20sleep%20is%20a%20basic%20human%20requirement%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20violated%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20said%20on%20Monday%20deprecating%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20questioning%20a%20senior%20citizen%20throughout%20the%20night%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-post-midnight-questioning-by-central-agency-bombay-high-courts-violation-of-rights-reminder-5448540%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-post-midnight-questioning-by-central-agency-bombay-high-courts-violation-of-rights-reminder-5448540%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-post-midnight-questioning-by-central-agency-bombay-high-courts-violation-of-rights-reminder-5448540%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%3A%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20now%20have%20'300'%20in%20sight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713250039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109336757%2Cimgsize-75908.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket