20For%20AI%20Women%20Is%20Announced%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EModels%20and%20influencers%20generated%20through%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20compete%20in%20a%20%26quot%3BMiss%20AI%26quot%3B%20beauty%20pageant%20with%20a%20prize%20money%20of%20%2420%2C000.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Flesliekatz%2F2024%2F04%2F15%2Ffirst-ai-beauty-pageant-to-crown-winner-based-on-looks-and-social-clout%2F%3Fsh%3D2ade429c1a55%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20is%20the%20world's%20first%20AI%20beauty%20pageant%20and%20the%20contestants%20will%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20looks%2C%20the%20heft%20they%20command%20online%20and%20the%20technical%20skill%20that%20went%20into%20creating%20them.%20The%20AI%20influencers'%20social%20clout%20will%20be%20assessed%20based%20on%20their%20engagement%20numbers%20with%20fans%2C%20rate%20of%20growth%20of%20audience%20and%20utilisation%20of%20platforms%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said%20citing%20a%20release%20from%20World%20AI%20Creator%20Awards%20(WAICA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pageant%20will%20see%20AI-generated%20ladies%20go%20head-to-head%20in%20front%20of%20a%20panel%20of%20judges%2C%20including%20two%20AI%20influencers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20contest%20is%20being%20organised%2C%20and%20more%20are%20planned%20on%20fashion%2C%20diversity%20and%20computer-generated%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20feature%20Fanvue%2C%20a%20subscription-based%20platform%20that%20hosts%20virtual%20models%2C%20as%20a%20partner%20of%20WAICA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20prize%20is%20%245%2C000%20cash%2C%20which%20will%20be%20given%20to%20Miss%20AI%20winner%20(or%20the%20creator%20behind%20it)%20along%20with%20Fanvue%20promotion%20and%20PR%20support.%20The%20runner-up%20and%20third%20place%20winner%20will%20also%20be%20awarded%20cash%20prizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winners%20will%20be%20announced%20on%20May%2010%2C%20with%20an%20online%20awards%20ceremony%20set%20to%20take%20place%20later%20in%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entries%20opened%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20judges%20in%20the%20four-member%20panel%20are%20AI-generated%3A%20Aitana%20Lopez%20from%20Spain%20with%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20followers%20and%20Emily%20Pellegrini%2C%20who%20has%20more%20than%20250%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20are%20humans%3A%20Andrew%20Bloch%2C%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20PR%20adviser%2C%20and%20Sally-Ann%20Fawcett%2C%20a%20beauty%20pageant%20historian%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20Misdemeanours%3A%20Beauty%20Queen%20Scandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20fast%20learning%20curve%20expanding%20my%20knowledge%20on%20AI%20creators%2C%20and%20it's%20quite%20incredible%20what%20is%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Ms%20Fawcett%20as%20saying%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20rules%2C%20entrants%20must%20be%20100%20per%20cent%20AI-generated%20and%20there%20are%20no%20restrictions%20on%20the%20tools%20used.%20%26quot%3BMiss%20AI%20welcomes%20creations%20produced%20from%20any%20type%20of%20generator%2C%20whether%20it's%20DeepAI%2C%20Midjourney%20or%20your%20own%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rules%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20website%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20thousands%20of%20entries%20have%20been%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713247080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgbiunlr_miss-ai-contest_625x300_16_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fworlds-first-miss-ai-contest-to-judge-winner-on-beauty-and-social-media-clout-5452442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pageant%20will%20see%20AI-generated%20ladies%20go%20head-to-head%20in%20front%20of%20a%20panel%20of%20judges%2C%20including%20two%20AI%20influencers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22