ighing%20only%201.6%20pounds%20and%20measuring%20about%204%20inches%20tall%2C%20caused%20some%20damage%20to%20the%20home's%20roof%20and%20floor.%20Homeowner%20Alejandro%20Otero%2C%20who%20was%20on%20vacation%20at%20the%20time%2C%20expressed%20his%20disbelief%20at%20the%20incident%20but%20was%20grateful%20no%20one%20was%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20tremendous%20sound.%20It%20almost%20hit%20my%20son.%20He%20was%20two%20rooms%20over%20and%20heard%20it%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alejandro%20Otero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlejandro%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwinknews.com%2F2024%2F03%2F15%2Fobject-crashes-through-naples-ceiling-floor%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWINK%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20was%20on%20vacation%20when%20his%20son%20called.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20ripped%20through%20the%20house%20and%20then%20made%20a%20big%20hole%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20on%20the%20ceiling%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alejandro.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20heard%20that%2C%20we%20were%20like%2C%20impossible%2C%20and%20then%20immediately%20I%20thought%20of%20a%20meteorite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20returning%20home%20sooner%20than%20expected%20from%20their%20journey%2C%20they%20discovered%20a%20cylindrical%20object%2C%20weighing%20close%20to%20two%20pounds%2C%20had%20punctured%20through%20the%20ceiling%20and%20ripped%20through%20the%20floor.%20Alejandro%20speculates%20it%20may%20have%20originated%20from%20outer%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20used%20to%20have%20a%20cylindrical%20shape%2C%20and%20you%20can%20tell%20by%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20top%20that%20it%20travelled%20in%20this%20direction%20through%20the%20atmosphere.%20Whatever%20you%20burned%2C%20created%20in%20this%20burn%2C%20and%20melted%20the%20metal%20over%20in%20this%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alejandro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWherever%20it%20came%20from%2C%20it%20scared%20the%20Otero%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20shaking.%20I%20was%20completely%20in%20disbelief.%20What%20are%20the%20chances%20of%20something%20landing%20on%20my%20house%20with%20such%20force%20to%20cause%20so%20much%20damage%3F%26quot%3B%20Alejandro%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20super%20grateful%20that%20nobody%20got%20hurt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713244500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fdtgu3318_space-object_625x300_16_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-confirms-object-that-destroyed-florida-home-was-space-junk-5452204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mystery%20was%20solved%20on%20Monday%20by%20NASA%2C%20which%20confirmed%20the%20object%20was%20a%20piece%20of%20space%20junk%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-confirms-object-that-destroyed-florida-home-was-space-junk-5452204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-confirms-object-that-destroyed-florida-home-was-space-junk-5452204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-confirms-object-that-destroyed-florida-home-was-space-junk-5452204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Airport%20Among%20Top%2010%20Busiest%20Airports%20In%20World.%20Check%20Rankings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20flying%20after%20the%20pandemic%2C%20making%20airports%20busier%20than%20ever.%20A%20report%20by%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mce-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afar.com%2Fmagazine%2Fthe-busiest-airports-in-the-world%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afar.com%2Fmagazine%2Fthe-busiest-airports-in-the-world%5C%22%3EAirports%20Council%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shows%20that%20in%202023%2C%208.5%20billion%20passengers%20took%20to%20the%20skies%20worldwide%20%E2%80%93%20a%20huge%20jump%20of%2027.2%25%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20surge%20in%20numbers%20means%20the%20world%20is%20almost%20back%20to%20pre-pandemic%20travel%20levels%2C%20with%20a%20recovery%20rate%20of%2093.8%25%20from%202019.%20The%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20Delhi%20has%20secured%2010th%20position%2C%20with%20a%20passenger%20traffic%20of%2072.2%20million%20flyers%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ETop%2010%20busiest%20Airports%20in%20the%20World%202023%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHartsfield-Jackson%20Atlanta%20International%20Airport%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Atlanta%20Airport%20has%20once%20again%20claimed%20the%20title%20of%20the%20world's%20busiest%20airport%2C%20with%20104.65%20million%20passengers%20in%202023%20%E2%80%93%20a%2012%25%20jump%20from%202022.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20still%205%25%20below%202019%20levels%2C%20marking%20a%20slow%20recovery%20from%20the%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EDubai%20International%20Airport%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DBX%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20has%20surged%20to%20second%20place%20for%20total%20passenger%20traffic%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20recent%20data.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20but%20it%20also%20leads%20the%20pack%20for%20international%20passenger%20volume.%20This%20remarkable%20second%20place%20is%20a%20huge%20leap%20from%20its%205th%20position%20in%202022%20and%2027th%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EDallas%E2%80%93Fort%20Worth%20International%20Airport%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20international%20airport%20comes%20next%20on%20the%20list%20with%2081.75%20million%20passengers%20in%202023.%20With%20five%20terminals%20and%20168%20gates%2C%20the%20DFW%20airport%20is%20like%20a%20small%20city%2C%20covering%20over%2026%20square%20miles.%20Recently%2C%20it%20secured%20a%20%2435%20million%20federal%20grant%20to%20build%20a%20zero-carbon%20electrical%20plant%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20make%20DFW%20achieve%20net-zero%20carbon%20emissions%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ELondon's%20Heathrow%20Airport%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELondon's%20Heathrow%20Airport%2C%20which%20handled%2079.2%20million%20passengers%20in%202023%2C%20is%20the%20primary%20international%20hub%20for%20the%20UK%20capital.%20It%20is%20spread%20across%20four%20terminals%20-%202%2C%203%2C%204%2C%20and%205%20(Terminal%201%20was%20closed%20in%202015).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ETokyo%20Haneda%20International%20Airport%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%20on%20the%20list%2C%20with%C2%A078.7%20million%20passenger%20traffic%2C%20is%C2%A0the%20Tokyo%20Haneda%20International%20Airport%20(HND).%20It%20also%20takes%20the%20prize%20for%20the%20most%20improved%20airport%20in%202023.%20Its%20passenger%20numbers%20skyrocketed%20by%2055%25%20compared%20to%202022%2C%20boosting%20it%20from%20the%2016th%20spot%20to%20the%205th%20place%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EDenver%20International%20Airport%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenver%20International%20Airport%20welcomed%2077.8%20million%20passengers%20last%20year.%20The%20DEN%20completed%20a%20capacity%20expansion%20project%20in%202022%2C%20adding%2039%20new%20gates.%20Now%2C%20the%20airport%20has%20a%20total%20of%2090%20gates%20across%20its%20three%20terminals%2C%C2%A0a%2030%25%20increase%20in%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EIstanbul%20Airport%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IST%20airport%20welcomed%2076%20million%20passengers%2C%20a%2046%25%20increase%20from%202019.%20Once%20fully%20completed%2C%20Istanbul%20Airport%20aims%20to%20handle%20up%20to%20200%20million%20travellers%20annually%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%203%20times%20the%20capacity%20of%20its%20predecessor%2C%20Ataturk%20International%20Airport%2C%20which%20closed%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ELos%20Angeles%20International%20Airport%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LAX%2C%20which%20handled%2075%20million%20passengers%20in%202023%2C%20is%20undergoing%20a%20significant%20makeover.%20The%20airport%20has%20begun%20several%20major%20construction%20projects%20aimed%20at%20easing%20traffic%20congestion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EChicago