2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109332068%2Cimgsize-53410.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalman-khan-house-firing-bhuj-police-hand-over-two-accused-to-mumbai-crime-branch-for-further-questioning%2Farticleshow%2F109332072.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109332072.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20latest%20update%20on%20the%20firing%20incident%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20Bandra%20residence%20reveals%20that%20the%20Bhuj%20Police%20disclosed%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20that%20the%20two%20suspected%20gunmen%20in%20their%20custody%20have%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20Crime%20Branch%20for%20ongoing%20investigation.%20The%20accused%2C%20Gupta%20and%20Pal%2C%20both%20hailing%20from%20Bihar%2C%20were%20apprehended%20through%20technical%20surveillance%20efforts%20by%20collaborative%20teams%20from%20Kutch-West%20and%20Mumbai%20police%20departments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalman-khan-house-firing-bhuj-police-hand-over-two-accused-to-mumbai-crime-branch-for-further-questioning%2Farticleshow%2F109332072.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Supreme%20Court%20Today%2C%20Hearing%20On%20100%25%20VVPAT%20Paper%20Slip%20Match%20For%20Votes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPetitions%20seeking%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20polled%20on%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20by%20matching%20them%20with%20VVPAT%20paper%20slips%20will%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today.%20This%20comes%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20which%20begins%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VVPAT%20--%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20--%20enables%20a%20voter%20to%20see%20if%20the%20vote%20was%20cast%20properly%20and%20went%20to%20the%20candidate%20he%2Fshe%20supports.%20The%20VVPAT%20generates%20a%20paper%20slip%20that%20is%20kept%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20and%20can%20be%20opened%20if%20there%20is%20a%20dispute.%20Amid%20the%20Opposition's%20questions%20and%20apprehensions%20regarding%20the%20EVM%20system%20of%20voting%2C%20the%20petitions%20call%20for%20cross-verification%20of%20every%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20system%2C%20VVPAT%20paper%20slips%20of%20five%20randomly-selected%20EVMs%20in%20each%20assembly%20constituency%20or%20each%20assembly%20segment%20in%20a%20parliamentary%20constituency%20are%20physically%20verified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20have%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20and%20activist%20Arun%20Kumar%20Agarwal.%20Mr%20Agarwal%20has%20sought%20the%20counting%20of%20all%20VVPAT%20slips.%20On%20April%201%2C%20the%20court%20had%20sought%20replies%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Centre%20on%20his%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADR's%20petition%20seeks%20the%20court's%20direction%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20that%20voters%20are%20able%20to%20verify%20through%20VVPATs%20that%20their%20vote%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcounted%20as%20recorded%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%20petition%20says%20that%20the%20requirement%20of%20voters%20verifying%20that%20their%20votes%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Brecorded%20as%20cast%26quot%3B%20is%20somewhat%20met%20when%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20is%20displayed%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds%20after%20pressing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20EVM%20through%20a%20transparent%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20vacuum%20in%20law%20as%20the%20ECI%20has%20provided%20no%20procedure%20for%20the%20voter%20to%20verify%20that%20her%20vote%20has%20been%20'counted%20as%20recorded'%20which%20is%20an%20indispensable%20part%20of%20voter%20verifiability.%20The%20failure%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20provide%20for%20the%20same%20is%20in%20the%20teeth%20of%20purport%20and%20object%20of%20the%20directions%20issued%20by%20this%20Court%20in...%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20versus%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(2013%20verdict)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20first%20came%20up%20in%202009%20when%20BJP%20leader%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20after%20his%20party's%20defeat%20in%20the%20general%20election.%20Mr%20Swamy%20sought%20directions%20to%20incorporate%20a%20system%20of%20paper%20trail%20in%20EVMs%20as%20a%20proof%20that%20a%20voter's%20vote%20for%20a%20particular%20candidate%20has%20been%20correctly%20recorded.%20The%20high%20court%20rejected%20the%20petition%20and%20Mr%20Swamy%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%20its%202013%20judgment%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bsatisfied%20that%20the%20'paper%20trail'%20is%20an%20indispensable%20requirement%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20confidence%20of%20the%20voters%20in%20the%20EVMs%20can%20be%20achieved%20only%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20'paper%20trail'.%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20system%20ensure%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20voting%20system.%20With%20an%20intent%20to%20have%20fullest%20transparency%20in%20the%20system%20and%20to%20restore%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20voters%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20set%20up%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20system%20because%20vote%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20act%20of%20expression%20which%20has%20immense%20importance%20in%20democratic%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20response%20to%20petitions%20seeking%20VVPAT%20verification%20of%20all%20votes%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20has%20pointed%20to%20manpower%20and%20infrastructure%20challenges%20and%20argued%20that%20such%20a%20step%20would%20delay%20the%20counting%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713240600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fjc8kolng_evm-and-vvpat_625x300_20_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-court-today-hearing-on-100-vvpat-paper-slip-match-for-votes-5451858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Petitions%20seeking%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20polled%20on%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20by%20matching%20them%20with%20VVPAT%20paper%20slips%20will%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-court-today-hearing-on-100-vvpat-paper-slip-match-for-votes-5451858%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-court-today-hearing-on-100-vvpat-paper-slip-match-for-votes-5451858%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-court-today-hearing-on-100-vvpat-paper-slip-match-for-votes-5451858%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFor%20The%20Sake%20Of%20IPL...%26quot%3B%3A%20Tennis%20Legend%20Writes%20To%20BCCI%2C%20Wants%20RCB%20Sold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tough%20day%20to%20be%20a%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20fan%20on%20Monday.%20Facing%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Faf%20du%20Plessis%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1579-faf-du-plessis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EFaf%20du%20Plessis%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0led%20side%20conceded%20287%20in%2020%20overs%20-%20the%20most%20in%20IPL's%20history.%20Though%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dinesh%20Karthik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F666-dinesh-karthik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDinesh%20Karthik%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20