eir%20prognosis%20can%20improve.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShannen%20Doherty%2C%20the%20actor%20best%20known%20for%20her%20role%20in%20%26quot%3BBeverly%20Hills%2C%2090210%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20stage%204%20cancer.%20She's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshannen-doherty-90210-declutter-downsize-breast-cancer-mom-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20rid%20of%20her%20material%20possessions%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20she%20can%20focus%20on%20spending%20time%20with%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20episode%20of%20her%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20Be%20Clear%20With%20Shannen%20Doherty%2C%26quot%3B%20released%20on%20April%201%2C%20the%20actor%20said%20she%20wants%20to%20sell%20off%20some%20of%20her%20stuff%20so%20her%20mother%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20dealing%20with%20it%20if%20she%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cancer%2C%20for%20me%2C%20has%20really%20made%20me%20take%20stock%20of%20my%20life%20and%20shift%20my%20priorities%2C%20and%20my%20priority%20at%20the%20moment%20is%20my%20mom%2C%26quot%3B%20Doherty%2C%2053%2C%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20her%20to%20have%20four%20storage%20units%20filled%20with%20furniture%20because%20I%20have%20a%20furniture%20obsession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20she%20hopes%20to%20use%20that%20money%20to%20travel%20with%20her%20mom%20without%20dipping%20into%20her%20savings.%20A%20representative%20for%20Doherty%20declined%20to%20provide%20additional%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoherty%20is%20one%20of%20several%20Hollywood%20stars%20who%20have%20used%20their%20public%20platforms%20to%20discuss%20the%20ways%20they're%20managing%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Michael%20Douglas%20said%20at%20a%20film%20festival%20panel%20that%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20tongue%20cancer%20in%202010%20taught%20him%20to%20appreciate%20his%20family%20more%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2F3am%2Fcelebrity-news%2Fmichael-douglas-says-beating-cancer-10192404%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Mirror%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20during%20an%20appearance%20on%20the%20British%20breakfast%20program%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXDb_9Rs3Oo4%26ab_channel%3DLorraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELorraine%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20March%2C%20Scottish%20comedian%20Janey%20Godley%20told%20host%20Lorraine%20Kelly%20that%20she%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Doherty%20%E2%80%94%20was%20also%20decluttering%20amid%20the%20recurrence%20of%20her%20ovarian%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20getting%20rid%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20clothes%2C%20I'm%20getting%20rid%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20old%20stuff%2C%20the%20charity%20shop%20loves%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Godley%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20paring%20everything%20down%20and%20getting%20everything%20ready%20so%20when%20I%20do%20go%2C%20it's%20not%20such%20a%20big%20trauma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETaking%20stock%20of%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDoherty%20was%20first%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%20in%202015%20and%20has%20spoken%20about%20her%20journey%20with%20the%20disease%20repeatedly%20on%20several%20public%20platforms%2C%20including%20on%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodmorningamerica.com%2Fculture%2Fstory%2Fshannen-doherty-shares-stage-breast-cancer-id-people-68737604%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGood%20Morning%20America%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20episode%20in%202020.%20Her%20comments%20about%20getting%20rid%20of%20physical%20belongings%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20new%20research%20that%20shows%20the%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-in-cancer-among-young-people-under-age-50-charts-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%20has%20risen%20sharply%20in%20the%20past%2030%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20researchers%20don't%20know%20why%20the%20rate%20is%20increasing%2C%20Doherty's%20move%20to%20declutter%20her%20life%20is%20typical%20of%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20often%20helpful%20for%20%E2%80%94%20people%20who%20are%20facing%20a%20serious%20medical%20diagnosis%2C%20two%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Jeffrey%20Peppercorn%2C%20a%20breast%20cancer%20medical%20oncologist%20and%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%20Cancer%20Supportive%20Care%20and%20Survivorship%20Program%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20advises%20his%20patients%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20things%20in%20life%20that%20are%20most%20important%20to%20them%20amid%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20their%20prognosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStage%20four%20breast%20cancer%20is%20not%20curable%2C%20but%20it%20is%20treatable%2C%20meaning%20that%20we%20can%20control%20the%20disease%20and%20prevent%20it%20from%20getting%20worse%2C%20often%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20'decluttering'%20your%20life%2C%20whether%20that%20means%20material%20possessions%20that%20you%20don't%20need%2C%20closets%20you%20have%20ignored%20for%20years%2C%20or%20things%20that%20you%20get%20stressed%20over%20that%20really%20aren't%20important%2C%20can%20be%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20for%20people%20to%20realize%20that%20certain%20material%20possessions%20aren't%20that%20important%20anymore%2C%20Amy%20Morin%2C%20a%20psychotherapist%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famymorinlcsw.com%2Fbooks-by-amy-morin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13%20Things%20Mentally%20Strong%20People%20Don't%20Do%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20might%20get%20rid%20of%20their%20tools%20as%20they%20realize%20they%20won't%20be%20restoring%20that%20antique%20car%20they%20dreamed%20about%2C%20or%20they%20might%20sell%20their%20boat%20as%20they%20no%20longer%20imagine%20a%20life%20on%20the%20lake%20where%20they%20go%20fishing%2C%26quot%3B%20Morin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20decluttering%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20with%20a%20serious%20illness%20often%20have%20little%20control%20over%20what's%20going%20on.%20But%20one%20thing%20they%20can%20control%20is%20their%20material%20possessions%2C%26quot%3B%20Morin%20said.%20%26quot%3BSelling%20things%2C%20sorting%20through%20items%2C%20and%20getting%20rid%20of%20stuff%20they%20no%20longer%20need%20may%20help%20them%20feel%20more%20in%20control%20over%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20rid%20of%20stuff%20might%20help%20someone%20feel%20like%20they're%20relieving%20their%20families%20from%20that%20burden%2C%20too%2C%20Morin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20things%20can%20continue%20to%20improve%2C%20Peppercorn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20want%20every%20patient%20that%20is%20newly%20diagnosed%20with%20stage%20four%20breast%20cancer%20to%20sell%20all%20of%20their%20possessions%2C%20because%20they%20may%20well%20find%20they%20are%20still%20alive%20and%20doing%20well%20four%2C%20five%2C%20or%20even%2010%20years%20or%20more%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Peppercorn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20that%2C%20he%20advises%20his%20patients%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20future%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20with%20serious%20or%20terminal%20illnesses%20might%20find%20it%20helpful%20to%20set%20goals%20or%20create%20a%20bucket%20list%2C%20Morin%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20their%20priorities%20shift%2C%20they%20may%20find%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20they%20really%20want%20to%20accomplish%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20without%20the%20same%20fears%20they%20might%20have%20once%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshannen-doherty-90210-methods-dealing-with-breast-cancer-experts-de