hemsworth-western-movie-1235971495%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20a%20Holi%20festival%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20tradition%20and%20contemporary%20celebration%20create%20a%20colorful%20union%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20throwing%20colored%20powder%20at%20each%20other%20while%20wearing%20all%20white.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618331e16bde8d4ead80ec5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAttendees%20gathered%20at%20a%20Holi%20celebration%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York%2C%20on%20March%2016%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Hindu%20festival%20Holi%20has%20become%20more%20popular%20and%20inclusive%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Indian%20diaspora.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAttendees%20at%20a%20celebration%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York%2C%20described%20coming%20together%20for%20the%20holiday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%C2%A0%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcommunity-in-focus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommunity%20in%20Focus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20highlighting%20Asian%20and%20Pacific%20Islander%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20festival%20of%20colors%2C%20observed%20as%20Holi%20in%20India%20and%20Fagu%20Purnima%20in%20Nepal%2C%20holds%20immense%20cultural%20significance%20for%20South%20Asians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20earliest%20memories%20of%20celebrating%20Holi%20as%20a%20child%20in%20India%20are%20vividly%20filled%20with%20hues%3B%20Indian%20delicacies%20like%20gujiya%2C%20dahi%20bhalle%20chaat%2C%20and%20gulab%20jamun%3B%20and%20jubilant%20moments%20shared%20with%20loved%20ones.%20Rising%20early%20on%20the%20festival%20day%2C%20I'd%20perform%20the%20ritual%20of%20applying%20oil%20all%20over%20my%20body%20and%20scalp%20to%20ward%20off%20any%20lingering%20color%20stains%20after%20the%20festivities.%20Outside%20our%20homes%2C%20a%20lively%20scene%20unfolded%20as%20kids%20gathered%20with%20various%20colored%20powders%20called%20gulal%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewater%20guns%2C%20and%20water%20balloons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20would%20make%20me%20and%20my%20elder%20brother%20wear%20the%20oldest%20pairs%20of%20pants%20she%20could%20find%20so%20that%20they%20could%20be%20discarded%20without%20objection.%20Both%20of%20us%20would%20fight%20to%20wear%20a%20white%20T-shirt%2C%20because%20wearing%20all-white%20clothes%20on%20Holi%20had%20been%20romanticized%20in%20Bollywood%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226628%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20holding%20his%20hands%20up%20to%20the%20camera%20with%20pink%20and%20green%20powder%20covering%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661944093f923f7dab073d78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Sheetal%20Banchariya%2C%20used%20to%20celebrate%20Holi%20in%20India%20and%20now%20enjoys%20the%20holiday%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20homesick%2C%20especially%20during%20festivals.%20I'm%20sure%20other%20immigrants%20can%20relate%3A%20Celebrating%20festivals%20in%20a%20foreign%20land%20hits%20differently%20and%20often%20takes%20you%20down%20memory%20lane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20of%20Asian%20Indians%20in%20the%20US%20has%20experienced%20remarkable%20growth%2C%20surging%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Flibrary%2Fstories%2F2023%2F09%2F2020-census-dhc-a-asian-population.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2050%25%20between%202010%20and%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reach%20a%20substantial%20total%20of%204.4%20million.%20With%20the%20growing%20population%2C%20the%20opportunities%20to%20get%20together%20as%20a%20community%20on%20special%20cultural%20occasions%20are%20increasing.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20always%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUma%20Kapoor%2C%2057%2C%20migrated%20to%20the%20US%20about%2035%20years%20ago%20after%20marrying%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20already%20worked%20in%20the%20country.%20Kapoor%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Queens%2C%20New%20York%2C%20recalled%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20occasions%20would%20come%20and%20go%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20wouldn't%20feel%20any%20festive%20vibes.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20not%20many%20or%20any%20events%20celebrating%20Holi%20at%20that%20time%2C%20despite%20a%20considerable%20number%20of%20Indians%20living%20in%20Jackson%20Heights%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226782%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20with%20brown%20curly%20hair%20wearing%20white%20hoodie%2C%20lei%2C%20sunglasses%20smiling%20and%20looking%20to%20the%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66182cf716bde8d4ead807a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224521%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUma%20Kapoor%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20over%20three%20decades%20ago%2C%20has%20noticed%20a%20greater%20presence%20of%20young%20Indians%20in%20NYC%20in%20recent%20years.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20celebrations%20begin%20two%20or%20even%20three%20weeks%20prior%20to%20the%20actual%20Holi.%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20commercial%20events%20popping%20up%20in%20Jersey%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20and%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20the%20increasing%20population%20of%20young%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kapoor%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20director%20in%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20IT%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20diaspora%20spreading%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20Holi%20has%20also%20evolved.%20In%20the%20heart%20of%20New%20York%20City%2C%20Manny%20Singh%2C%20an%20event%20manager%2C%20has%20been%20fostering%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20among%20people%20from%20different%20cultures%2C%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20ethnicities.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20started%20organizing%20an%20event%20called%20Holi%20in%20the%20City%20as%20a%20way%20for%20brown%20people%20to%20enjoy%20the%20celebration%20while%20they%20were%20away%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20event%20has%20been%20hosted%20at%20Brooklyn's%20Bk%20Backyard%20Bar%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20owner%2C%20Jarrod%20Fox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20throwing%20pink%20and%20green%20powder%20at%20outdoor%20Holi%20festival.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661833f43f923f7dab07064d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFestivalgoers%20threw%20beautiful%20hues%20of%20gulal%20as%20onlookers%20cheered.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAkash%20Sheth%2C%2031%2C%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20City%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year%20ago%20with%20his%20wife%20to%20work%20at%20Google.%20Celebrating%20their%20first%20Holi%20in%20the%20US%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20attend%20Singh's%20event%20in%20Brooklyn.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20sense%20of%20nostalgia%20mingled%20with%20excitement%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheth%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20way%20of%20reconnecting%20with%20my%20roots%20and%20sharing%20the%20joy%20of%20Holi%20with%20a%20diverse%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20who%20migrated%20to%20the%20US%20about%20four%20decades%20ago%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20said%20that%20for%20him%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20about%20more%20than%20just%20colors.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20over%20the%20years%20he'd%20seen%20Indians%2C%20Pakistanis%2C%20Nepalese%2C%20Bhutanese%2C%20Sri%20Lankans%2C%20African%20Americans%2C%20and%20Irish%20people%20attending%20his%20Holi%20event.%20%26quot%3BThe%20segment%20that%20is%20interested%20in%20celebrating%20Holi%20are%20more%20people%20of%20non-South%20Asian%20background%20because%20they%20see%20it%20on%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20celebrations%20are%20now%20basically%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20cultures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElise%20Young%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20fitness%20professional%20who%20founded%20Elise's%20Bodyshop%2C%20and%20her%20wife%2C%20Carmen%20Perez%2C%20a%20financial-services%20professional%20turned%20tech%20entrepreneur%2C%20have%20been%20together%20for%20nine%20years%20and%20got%20married%20six%20years%20ago.%20This%20year%20they%20traveled%20from%20Connecticut%20to%20celebrate%20their%20first%20Holi%20together%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20fascinating%20to%20me%20is%20that%20everyone%20from%20all%20different%20backgrounds%20is%20on%20the%20same%20page%2C%26quot%3B%20Young%2C%20who's%20originally%20from%20Massachusetts%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20here%20just%20for%20good%20vibes%2C%20celebration%2C%20uplifting%20and%20positive%20energy.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20your%20age%2C%20sex%2C%20gender%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20women%20cheek%20to%20cheek%20smiling%20at%20the%20camera%20with%20pink%20and%20orange%20powder%20on%20their%20faces.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66182ddc1caec1275a6f3f38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECarmen%20Perez%20and%20Elise%20Young%2C%20who%20are%20married%2C%20celebrated%20Holi%20at%20Singh's%20event.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHoli%20celebrations%20have%20gained%20popularity%20outside%20India%20partly%20because%20Holi%20is%20perceived%20and%20celebrated%20as%20a%20fun%20carnival%20%E2%80%94%20unlike%20Diwali%2C%20which%20is%20celebrated%20as%20a%20religious%20event.%20%26quot%3BHoli%20is%20more%20of%20an%20activity%20than%20a%20festival%2C%20and%20that%20activity%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20dance%20and%20music%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapoor%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20also%20started%20enjoying%20Bollywood%20music%20because%20of%20the%20beats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVijay%20Satnarine%2C%20the%20director%20of%20education%20for%20the%20Hindu%20American%20Foundation%2C%20has%20an%20explanation%20for%20the%20festival's%20inclusivity.%20Holi%20marks%20the%20arrival%20of%20spring%20and%20the%20end%20of%20winter.%20It's%20celebrated%20on%20the%20full-moon%20day%2C%20Purnima%2C%20in%20the%20Hindu%20month%20of%20Phalguna%2C%20which%20usually%20falls%20in%20February%20or%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnset%20of%20spring%2C%20the%20burning%20of%20the%20chaff%2C%20roasting%20the%20green%20chickpeas%20in%20the%20fire%2C%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20bonfire%20because%20of%20the%20full%20moon%20and%20using%20the%20ashes%20of%20the%20bonfire%20just%20to%20throw%20around%20in%20celebration%20of%20the%20spring%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20festival%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Satnarine%2C%20who%20has%20taught%20Hindu%20dharma%20traditions%20to%20university%20students%20in%20London%2C%20Wales%2C%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20and%20man%20embracing%20with%20colored%20powder%20on%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66182ff916bde8d4ead80a07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELove%20was%20in%20the%20air%20at%20the%20Holi%20celebration.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20two%20prominent%20Hindu%20legends%20associated%20with%20the%20festival.%20One%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20Prahlad%2C%20a%20devotee%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu%2C%20whose%20tyrant%20father%2C%20King%20Hiranyakashipu%2C%20wanted%20everyone%20to%20worship%20him.%20When%20Prahlad%20refused%20and%20continued%20to%20worship%20Lord%20Vishnu%2C%20Hiranyakashipu's%20sister%2C%20Holika%2C%20attempted%20to%20burn%20Prahlad%20alive.%20Because%20Holika%20was%20immune%20to%20fire%2C%20Prahlad%20was%20placed%20on%20the%20lap%20of%20his%20aunt%20while%20she%20sat%20atop%20a%20blazing%20pyre.%20But%20Prahlad%20emerged%20unharmed%20while%20Holika%20perished%2C%20symbolizing%20the%20victory%20of%20good%20over%20evil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20legend%20revolves%20around%20the%20playful%20love%20story%20of%20Radha%20Rani%20and%20Lord%20Krishna.%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20envious%20of%20Radha's%20fair%20complexion%2C%20teasingly%20colored%20her%20face%2C%20initiating%20the%20ritual%20of%20playing%20with%20gulal%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crowd%20around%20a%20dance%20group%20at%20a%20Holi%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661830a316bde8d4ead80a49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMusic%20and%20dancing%20helped%20bring%20the%20Brooklyn%20festival%20to%20life.%3Cp%3EZayira%20Ray%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20alive%20the%20practice%2C%20rooted%20in%20ancient%20Hindu%20mythology%2C%20of%20celebrating%20Holi%20with%20colors%2C%20Singh%20makes%20color%20powders%20available%20for%20all%20the%20attendees%20at%20his%20events.%20He%20also%20provides%20live%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Holi%20transcends%20geographical%20boundaries%2C%20it%20serves%20as%20a%20celebration%20of%20a%20new%20season%20and%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20unity%20among%20diverse%20cultures%20and%20communities.%20From%20the%20bustling%20streets%20of%20India%20to%20the%20vibrant%20neighborhoods%20of%20the%20Big%20Apple%2C%20Holi's%20essence%20remains%3A%20a%20jubilant%20occasion%20that%20fosters%20camaraderie%2C%20joy%2C%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20togetherness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%