Shalini.%20So%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20to%20look%20for%20properties%20around%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20duo%20first%20came%20across%20the%20land%20where%20their%20home%20stands%20now%2C%20they%20were%20taken%20aback%20by%20its%20beauty%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looked%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20painting!%20%E2%80%9CSince%20then%20we%20have%20built%20the%20property%20piece%20by%20piece%2C%20pouring%20our%20hearts%20into%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20features%20four%20bedrooms%20%E2%80%94%20each%20named%20after%20one%20of%20the%20four%20seasons%20of%20the%20year.%C2%A0%20The%20%E2%80%98Spring%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Summer%E2%80%99%20rooms%20are%20situated%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20whereas%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Autumn%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Winter%E2%80%99%20rooms%20are%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20room%20opens%20up%20to%20magnificent%20views%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302828%2Fbest-must-take-winter-treks-in-himalayas-uttarakhand-views-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Himalayas%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Beas%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20expect%20at%20the%20Homestay%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rooms%20do%20not%20have%20TV%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shalini%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20anybody%20would%20want%20to%20sit%20in%20their%20room%20watching%20TV%20when%20you%20can%20sit%20outdoors%20in%20the%20orchard%20and%20enjoy%20the%20views.%20There%20are%20flowers%2C%20butterflies%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20all%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuests%20can%20also%20take%20hikes%20up%20the%20hills%20or%20serene%20walks%20along%20the%20river%20and%20to%20nearby%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20huge%20riverside%20area%20with%20a%20tiny%20%E2%80%98beach%E2%80%99.%2