0far%20over%20150%20livestock%20corrals%20have%20been%20built%20across%20Ladakh%2C%20benefitting%20more%20than%20600%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20homestay%20concept%20enables%20the%20villagers%20to%20earn.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20200%20homestays%20across%2040%20villages%20of%20Ladakh%20under%20the%20conservancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20model%2C%20he%20shares%20that%20choosing%20to%20stay%20in%20one%20of%20these%20homestays%20generates%20funds%20for%20communities%20that%20they%20use%20to%20protect%20their%20mountain%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20funds%20are%20created%20in%20a%20unique%20way%3A%2010%20percent%20of%20all%20homestays%E2%80%99%20income%20goes%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98village%20conservation%20fund%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20villagers%20for%20tree%20planting%2C%20garbage%20cleaning%2C%20and%20maintenance%20of%20their%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20such%20as%20mani%20walls%2C%20%3Cem%3Echortens%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20sacred%20juniper%20stands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344962%2Fhow-to-start-a-homestay-in-india-rules-tips-from-owners-travel-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillagers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20host%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20done%20so%20that%20no%20single%20family%20can%20monopolise%20the%20tourists.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20a%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Namgail%20shares%2C%20the%20tourism%20model%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20that%20people%20across%20the%20Himalayas%20have%20taken%20inspiration%20from%20it%20and%20are%20replicating%20it.%20But%20regulation%20is%20important%2C%20he%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20evening%20settles%20over%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20snow%20is%20tinged%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20blue%20and%20orange%2C%20a%20blend%20of%20the%20hues%20of%20the%20setting%20sun%20and%20dusk.%20As%20the%20locals%20go%20into%20their%20homes%2C%20bolt%20their%20doors%2C%20and%20warn%20the%20children%20to%20stay%20inside%2C%20the%20silent%20rustle%20of%20leaves%20goes%20unheard.%20So%20does%20the%20slither%20in%20the%20bushes%20and%20the%20shadow%20of%20a%20feline%20beginning%20its%20prowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712827631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--1711367266.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%2C%20established%20by%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20and%20led%20by%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20champions%20the%20harmonious%20coexistence%20of%20villagers%20and%20snow%20leopards%20in%20Ladakh%20through%20its%20insurance%20schemes%20and%20sustainable%20tourism%20initiatives%2C%20fostering%20ecological%20balance%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345716%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-tsewang-namgail-himalayan-homestays-ladakh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Never%20Got%20to%20Read%E2%80%99%3A%2074-YO%20Grandmother%20Runs%20a%20Unique%20%E2%80%98Book%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20With%205000%20Books!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClinking%20utensils%2C%20the%20gentle%20brewing%20of%20tea%2C%20and%20the%20lively%20chatter%20of%20people%20eagerly%20awaiting%20their%20food%20create%20a%20vibrant%20ambience%20within%20the%20eatery.%20Normally%2C%20the%20entire%20space%20is%20imbued%20with%20the%20tantalising%20aroma%20of%20delicious%20meals%20being%20prepared%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20However%2C%20this%20delightful%20scent%20often%2