Pallabi%20Ghosh%20was%2012%20years%20old%2C%20she%20encountered%20her%20first%20case%20of%20a%20child%20from%20a%20nearby%20village%20being%20trafficked.%20This%20shaped%20her%20decision%20to%20dedicate%20her%20life%20to%20rescuing%20children%20who%20were%20victims%20of%20this%20horrific%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%2C%20Pallabi%20founded%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313315%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-rescue-children-from-trafficking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImpact%20and%20Dialogue%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20through%20which%20she%20has%20rescued%20over%2010%2C000%20children%2C%20who%20would%20otherwise%20fall%20prey%20to%20human%20trafficking%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20other%20accompanying%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20she%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20rescuing%20the%20kids%20is%20not%20enough.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20rehabilitate%20them%20or%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20re-trafficking.%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20a%20foundation%20of%20my%20own%20that%20would%20not%20only%20rescue%20but%20also%20empower%20these%20children.%E2%80%9D%20But%20what%20will%20be%20a%20transformative%20step%2C%20shares%20Pallabi%2C%20is%20sensitising%20constables%20to%20these%20social%20evils%20as%20they%20are%20the%20first%20responders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallabi%20shares%20that%20her%20scope%20of%20work%20includes%20reaching%20out%20to%2015%20new%20villages%20every%20month.%20Spread%20across%20India%2C%20these%20include%20Kharimachan%2C%20Jarangdisha%2C%20Lengra%20Basti%20and%20Nyazat%20among%20others.%20In%20these%20villages%2C%20she%20works%20with%20groups%20of%20women%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20hundreds%20to%20give%20them%20access%20to%20livelihood%20and%20skill%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20maintain%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20impacted%20thousands%20of%20women%20if%20I%20had%20been%20insistent%20on%20podiums%20and%20properly%20executed%20events.%20I%20managed%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325386%2Fchangemakers-transform-polluted-water-bodies-idbi-bank-environment-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20huge%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20because%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20people%20personally%2C%20knocking%20one%20door%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20give%20the%20survivors%20a%20better%20life%2C%20Pallabi%20provides%20counselling%20services%2C%20upskilling%20sessions%20and%20more%20as%20she%20believes%20the%20children%20and%20women%20who%20are%20rescued%20need%20a%20brighter%20future%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20scope%20of%20Pallabi%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20work%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5UzKWto5Ui%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5UzKWto5Ui%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%