0officer%20and%20bears%20all%20the%20household%20responsibilities%20along%20with%20the%20college%20fees%20of%20her%20younger%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20became%20possible%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Samit%20Carr%20sir.%20Firstly%2C%20his%20organisation%20bore%20our%20mother%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20cost%20of%20Rs%203.6%20lakh.%20Then%2C%20he%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20nursing%20by%20getting%20a%20BSc%20degree.%20He%20also%20fought%20to%20get%20us%20a%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20from%20the%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Laxmi%2C%20the%20Jharkhand-based%20non-profit%2C%20Occupational%20Safety%20And%20Health%20Association%20of%20Jharkhand%20(OSHAJ)%2C%20led%20by%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%2C%20has%20helped%20at%20least%2050%20kin%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20get%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20he%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20kin%20of%2022%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20in%20West%20Bengal%20get%20a%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20each%2C%20and%2030%20silicosis-affected%20workers%20with%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each.%20In%20addition%2C%20Rs%2010%20crore%20funds%20were%20sanctioned%20for%20pension%20and%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20he%20has%20been%20actively%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20the%2068-year-old%20activist%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20is%20fighting%20authorities%20to%20help%20families%20cope%20with%20financial%20distress%20caused%20by%20the%20incurable%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-17111188