22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20aid%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20Bluetooth%2C%20and%20uses%20bone%20conduction%20technology.%20The%20hearing%20aid%2C%20which%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20band%2C%20sits%20behind%20the%20ear%20on%20the%20temporal%20bone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20device%20uses%20the%20bone%20as%20a%20conductor%20of%20sound.%20The%20device%2C%20placed%20on%20the%20temporal%20bone%2C%20sends%20vibrations%20to%20the%20cochlea.%20It%20bypasses%20the%20physical%20ear%20system%2C%20namely%20the%20outer%20ear%2C%20inner%20ear%20and%20middle%20ear%2C%20directly%20simulating%20the%20last%20part%20of%20the%20ear%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20brain%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Kanishk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20band%2C%20which%20the%20user%20wears%20on%20the%20hand%2C%20is%20equipped%20with%20microprocessors.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20captures%20the%20audio%20and%20sounds%2C%20tunes%20them%2C%20processes%20them%20and%20sends%20them%20to%20the%20hearing%20device%2C%20enabling%20the%20user%20to%20hear.%20The%20Bluetooth%20can%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20other%20device%20like%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20TV%2C%20or%20laptop%2C%20helping%20children%20listen%20to%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%20is%20usually%20a%20surgical%20implant%20called%20the%20BAHA%20implant%20(Bone-Anchored%20Hearing%20Aid)%2C%20which%20uses%20the%20same%20technology%20used%20in%20this%20hearing%20aid.%20The%20corresponding%20surgery%20generally%20costs%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20while%20this%20device%20costs%20Rs%2080%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20differentiator%20and%20patent%20is%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20use%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20the%20surgery%20and%20military%20devices%2C%20for%20a%20non-surgical%20hearing%20aid%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%